description:
Rick Howard is the author of the well-known book “The Omega Rebellion.” In this lecture he helps us to see how a strange teaching has come into God’s church and deceived many. Spiritual formation is a Jesuit teaching; Ignatius Loyola received his thirteen spiritual exercises supernaturally. Who gave him the spiritual exercises? Rick Howard raises the question, Why do the five leaders of the One Project have major positions in Seventh-day Adventist colleges? He presents the evidence that suggests there was a Jesuit infiltration of the SDA church.

For more please visit:
